data.event: Rock Island was officially incorporated on November 3, 1930.

event.title: arrived with a crew of men in 1887

data.event: As the first permanent settler to the Rock Island area, James Keane arrived with a crew of men in 1887.

event.title: Four years later, the Great Northern Railroad made

data.event: Four years later, the Great Northern Railroad made its first survey of the area and began construction toward the valley from the east.
